{% block body %}
    <div class="container">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-updates">How to get your studio data updated or added</a></li>
            <li><a href="#commissions-status-tracking">Automatic updates of commissions status</a></li>
            <li><a href="#keep-in-touch">Keep in touch, see what's going on, join the party</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h1 id="introduction">Awoo!</h1>

        <div class="container py-4">
            <p>
                Welcome to an <strong>incubating project</strong>. The ultimate goal is to make furries rule
                the world, but first things first, we need more fursuits, and this is what this website is
                about. Since this project is <strong>just starting</strong>, there is not much data here,
                nor functionalities. Hopefully this will change over time.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h1 id="data-updates">
            Include/update studio's data <small><span class="badge badge-warning">(makers love this!)</span></small>
        </h1>

        <div class="container py-4">
            <p>
                If you want your studio to be included in this list or some data to be updated (spelling of
                the name, links, types, anything), feel free to
                <a href="https://goo.gl/forms/6qoHxk8i2WsTKhjO2">fill in this questionnaire</a>.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="commissions-status-tracking">
            Automatic tracking and updates of commissions status
        </h2>

        <div class="container py-4">
            <p>
                This website can track and update the status of commissions for your studio - if they're open or closed.
                You don't need to remember to update this information here at all! There are a few need-to-knows:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>You need to actually keep at least <strong>one other</strong> website with up-to-date status</li>
                <li>
                    Not all kinds of websites are supported (yet) - sorry!
                    <ul>
                        <li>Generic websites (including Wix.com) - should work</li>
                        <li>FurAffinity with logging in restriction - nope</li>
                        <li>FurAffinity <strong>user page main info</strong> - yes, and recommended!</li>
                        <li>FurAffinity <strong>anything else, including journals</strong> - nope</li>
                        <li>Twitter - yes, but only profile info</li>
                        <li>Facebook - somehow... but discouraged!</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Approximate delay between update on your website and status getting updated here is between
                    6-24 hours, but this is <strong>not guaranteed</strong> everyday
                </li>
                <li>Contact me for "inclusion" and guidance in case of any doubts/problems</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

